com.amplifyframework.datastore.model

Interface ModelFieldTypeConverter<S,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The source type (e.g. SQLite's Cursor)
    T - The target type, usually the Model
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SQLiteModelFieldTypeConverter

    public interface ModelFieldTypeConverter<S,T>
    Establishes how `Model` fields should be converted to and from different targets (e.g. SQL and GraphQL).

    • Method Summary
